I am extremely interested in this research! Through this system, I have discovered a lot of songs I enjoy in the generated music playlist. It also allows me to explore different musical genres, preventing me from being confined to just one type. This is truly a fantastic feature, especially compared to other music recommendation systems that tend to suggest only a limited range of song types.

However, I still have some questions about the system. I wonder if the provided songs are primarily focused on works from a few years ago, with fewer selections from the latest music. If it could combine both new and older songs to create a more comprehensive recommendation playlist, I believe that would be a very promising direction for improvement.
